cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.DC

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with cross-lingual transfer for dependency parsing. It may also belong to cs.LG (Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it involves machine learning techniques for natural language processing. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it uses neural networks for the transfer method. Finally, it could be classified under cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) as it involves parallel processing of treebanks.
